        "subject": "LU-10938 wbc: Only request update bit on lookup with trybits",
        "message": "LU-10938 wbc: Only request update bit on lookup with trybits\n\nIn the face of an EX lock on the child, use a trylock to avoid\npreemptive cache flushing unless absolutely necessary.\nSo that if there is an EX lock on a client, do not disturb it\nunnecessarily.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nChange-Id: I092c5d3cdeaeb7343075bec32038ee12f8b7b093\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
